comments.body:
@haircommander I think maybe you're just trying to temporarily get to the system tests sooner, for faster cycling/debugging purposes?

The easiest way to do this is going through and adding/changing `skip: $CI == $CI` to the tasks you don't want.  Though I don't recommend doing this to the main `build_task` for (hopefully) obvious reasons :smile:  It should work with nearly every other task in `.cirrus.yml`.

@edsantiago FYI ^^^
